subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Fred Funk moved into position for his first major victory on the Champions Tour, shooting a bogey-free seven-under 65 to take a one-stroke lead over Jay Haas after the third round of the Jeld-Wen Tradition in Sunriver, Ore. Funk’s total was 16-under 200.
